NG0177:136: badzra thod phreng rat+na thod phreng rtsal //
NG0177:137: pad+ma thod phreng karma thod phreng rtsal //
NG0177:138: rdo rje mos pa rtsal dang myu gu rtsal //

NG0177:149: shakya seng+ge rdo rje grau bo lod //

NG0177:159: dbang chen nyi ma gser gyi nyi ma dang *//

NG0177:161: ro langs bde ba rdo rje thog rgod 'bar //

NG0177:167: mkha' 'gro nyi zla stong gi thod phreng can //
NG0177:168: yab yum gnyis kyi cho 'phrul 'khor gyi tshogs //

NG0177:283: de ltar byin brlab lnga ldan pa'i //
NG0177:284: rnal 'byor spyod pa rmad du byung *//
